{{flavour|This spell hurls a bolt containing fiery energy; on piercing a target, it lets loose an explosion that harms nearby creatures as well.}}

'''Explosive Bolt''' is a level 6 spell only available through a [[rod of ignition]]. Each target it hits will cause a 3Ã—3 explosion on the target, as through struck by [[Fireball]].

While it doesn't have perfect accuracy, it can tear through a cramped group of opponents. Also note that the explosions can hurt you, so try to avoid using it against melee opponents.

==History==
*Explosive Bolt was removed in [[0.20]], along with [[rod]]s.
*Explosive Bolt was added in [[0.14]].
